dismissed from the party for denouncing widespread toplevel 
corruption and accusing party leaders of cultivating a personality 
cult around mugabe tekere helped found mugabes party in 1963 and 
was a member of its policymaking politburo he has promised an 
honest democratic and efficient government and said he will mount 
the first challenge to the presidency in national elections to be 
held by april 1990 the 10th anniversary of zimbabwes 
independence from britain 
