had died in washington 
he was a rare human being and we are all richer for his 
presence among us martinez said we will miss him very much 
pepper represented the 18th congressional district which covers 
most of miami and all of miami beach bal harbour and key biscayne 
its center is miamis heavily cuban eighth street or calle ocho 
and 50 percent of the district is hispanic 
a special election will be held to fill peppers seat but it 
could not be held for at least 40 days because of the minimum 
intervals for filing and two primary elections that would have to 
be held 
tributes came from all over florida which pepper watched grow 
from mostly rural land into the nations fourth mostpopulous state 
and which became home to many of the senior citizens whose cause he 
championed 
he always said it was the senior citizens who made this 
country great said leila johnson a resident of mildred and 
