doubloons inscribed with his picture like the souvenir coins 
thrown from the floats in the mardi gras parade 
then everything was lovely dejan recalls while we waited 
to get our passports back the immigration people let me walk 
outside by the fence and pick up some holy rocks from the holy 
land 
