<TEXT>
gail gentry whose lower back was crushed when 
a mine roof caved in 11 years ago pushed his wheelchair in front 
of a caravan of massive coal trucks and held a sign saying 
pittston stole my health card 
im taking a stand against an immoral company and against an 
