union will face daily fines ranging from 20000 to 100000 if the 
tactics continue 
a federal judge is scheduled to decide thursday whether to issue 
his own restrictions on strike activities based on a complaint 
filed by the national labor relations board which accused the 
union of unfair labor practices 
